  ('87c026a0-c375-49ff-a3eb-2b37dac53e04-ex2', '87c026a0-c375-49ff-a3eb-2b37dac53e04', 'left', 'The withdrawal of foreign capital left the banking sector acutely vulnerable to liquidity shocks.', '外资撤离使银行业极易受到流动性冲击。'),
  ('169d06c4-955d-4ae5-af9f-b47a3b686f8c-ex1', '169d06c4-955d-4ae5-af9f-b47a3b686f8c', 'meeting', 'The meeting starts at ten.', '会议十点开始。'),
  ('169d06c4-955d-4ae5-af9f-b47a3b686f8c-ex2', '169d06c4-955d-4ae5-af9f-b47a3b686f8c', 'meeting', 'The emergency meeting concluded with a joint communiqué pledging coordinated fiscal action.', '紧急会议以一份承诺协调财政行动的联合公报告终。'),
