  ('2794537a-c8a9-4540-8731-47d31423ee90-ex2', '2794537a-c8a9-4540-8731-47d31423ee90', 'determine', 'The arbitral tribunal must determine whether the expropriation was conducted lawfully.', '仲裁庭必须裁定这次征收是否合法进行。'),
  ('dd3fea44-80ce-417e-b8e5-6e3098a2d301-ex1', 'dd3fea44-80ce-417e-b8e5-6e3098a2d301', 'prepare', 'I need to prepare for tomorrow''s exam.', '我需要为明天的考试做准备。'),
  ('dd3fea44-80ce-417e-b8e5-6e3098a2d301-ex2', 'dd3fea44-80ce-417e-b8e5-6e3098a2d301', 'prepare', 'Member states were instructed to prepare contingency plans for a disorderly market exit.', '成员国被要求为无序退出市场的情形准备应急预案。'),
  ('d03bff00-1a1f-42de-be4c-2bf010738890-ex1', 'd03bff00-1a1f-42de-be4c-2bf010738890', 'disease', 'Washing hands helps prevent disease.', '洗手有助于预防疾病。'),
  ('d03bff00-1a1f-42de-be4c-2bf010738890-ex2', 'd03bff00-1a1f-42de-be4c-2bf010738890', 'disease', 'The surveillance network enables early detection of infectious disease outbreaks.', '该监测网络能够及早发现传染病疫情。'),
  ('8de675a1-5fb3-4e38-b098-fd484fe52be1-ex1', '8de675a1-5fb3-4e38-b098-fd484fe52be1', 'whatever', 'Order whatever you like.', '你想点什么就点什么。'),
