  ('7a900c3b-74ec-4ada-a173-4fc8b62f0f34-ex2', '7a900c3b-74ec-4ada-a173-4fc8b62f0f34', 'success', 'The program''s success hinges on sustained cooperation among historically rival agencies.', '该项目的成功取决于历来相互竞争的机构间的持续合作。'),
  ('d989eced-ec88-4dd7-8375-c079bb8cdf4b-ex1', 'd989eced-ec88-4dd7-8375-c079bb8cdf4b', 'argue', 'Let''s not argue about small things.', '我们别为小事争吵了。'),
  ('d989eced-ec88-4dd7-8375-c079bb8cdf4b-ex2', 'd989eced-ec88-4dd7-8375-c079bb8cdf4b', 'argue', 'Counsel will argue that the contested statute exceeds the legislature''s constitutional mandate.', '律师将主张，争议法规超出了立法机关的宪法授权。'),
  ('421d83ba-e919-4678-a12f-78544ddc3719-ex1', '421d83ba-e919-4678-a12f-78544ddc3719', 'cup', 'Would you like a cup of tea?', '你想来杯茶吗？'),
  ('421d83ba-e919-4678-a12f-78544ddc3719-ex2', '421d83ba-e919-4678-a12f-78544ddc3719', 'cup', 'The national team''s victory in the cup final prompted celebrations across the country.', '国家队在杯赛决赛中获胜，举国上下一片欢腾。'),
  ('c8c1471e-ba84-4849-be36-ea4aac723bec-ex1', 'c8c1471e-ba84-4849-be36-ea4aac723bec', 'particularly', 'I particularly enjoyed the dessert.', '我特别喜欢那道甜点。'),
  ('c8c1471e-ba84-4849-be36-ea4aac723bec-ex2', 'c8c1471e-ba84-4849-be36-ea4aac723bec', 'particularly', 'The downturn proved particularly damaging to regions dependent on a single industry.', '事实证明，经济下行对依赖单一产业的地区破坏尤为严重。'),
  ('d7397332-5d34-4af9-afd4-03104ef3d586-ex1', 'd7397332-5d34-4af9-afd4-03104ef3d586', 'amount', 'Add a small amount of salt.', '加少量盐。'),
  ('d7397332-5d34-4af9-afd4-03104ef3d586-ex2', 'd7397332-5d34-4af9-afd4-03104ef3d586', 'amount', 'The settlement requires repayment of the full amount together with accrued interest.', '和解协议要求连同应计利息全额偿还。'),
  ('44338f53-2279-4256-8249-fc6c3b1c7229-ex1', '44338f53-2279-4256-8249-fc6c3b1c7229', 'ability', 'She has the ability to learn quickly.', '她有快速学习的能力。'),
  ('44338f53-2279-4256-8249-fc6c3b1c7229-ex2', '44338f53-2279-4256-8249-fc6c3b1c7229', 'ability', 'The stress tests assess each institution''s ability to withstand severe market disruptions.', '压力测试评估每家机构抵御严重市场动荡的能力。'),
