  ('632b3590-5963-4005-8a0c-ab80ffbb2d05-ex2', '632b3590-5963-4005-8a0c-ab80ffbb2d05', 'staff', 'The inquiry found that staff had repeatedly raised safety concerns that management ignored.', '调查发现，员工曾多次提出安全隐患，但管理层置之不理。'),
  ('69e5013b-b4a9-4756-b0ae-1f2fdc91da9a-ex1', '69e5013b-b4a9-4756-b0ae-1f2fdc91da9a', 'recognize', 'I didn''t recognize you with your new haircut.', '你换了发型我都没认出来。'),
  ('69e5013b-b4a9-4756-b0ae-1f2fdc91da9a-ex2', '69e5013b-b4a9-4756-b0ae-1f2fdc91da9a', 'recognize', 'Several governments moved formally to recognize the newly constituted transitional authority.', '多国政府正式承认了新组建的过渡当局。'),
  ('914624e0-edc9-4234-ae4e-30a787f2873f-ex1', '914624e0-edc9-4234-ae4e-30a787f2873f', 'indicate', 'The arrow indicates the exit.', '箭头指示出口方向。'),
  ('914624e0-edc9-4234-ae4e-30a787f2873f-ex2', '914624e0-edc9-4234-ae4e-30a787f2873f', 'indicate', 'Preliminary data indicate a substantial decline in transmission following the intervention.', '初步数据表明，干预之后传播率大幅下降。'),
  ('ca767924-be20-44ff-95cd-a67221f37430-ex1', 'ca767924-be20-44ff-95cd-a67221f37430', 'character', 'She is the main character in the story.', '她是故事的主角。'),
  ('ca767924-be20-44ff-95cd-a67221f37430-ex2', 'ca767924-be20-44ff-95cd-a67221f37430', 'character', 'The proceedings will examine the fundamentally deceptive character of the marketing scheme.', '诉讼将审查该营销方案根本上的欺骗性质。'),
  ('26f9292b-ec7e-4ed1-93c4-93b7e515b745-ex1', '26f9292b-ec7e-4ed1-93c4-93b7e515b745', 'growth', 'The growth of this plant is very fast.', '这种植物长得很快。'),
  ('26f9292b-ec7e-4ed1-93c4-93b7e515b745-ex2', '26f9292b-ec7e-4ed1-93c4-93b7e515b745', 'growth', 'Sustained economic growth has lifted millions out of poverty across the region.', '持续的经济增长使该地区数百万人摆脱了贫困。'),
  ('65808bc3-03ff-4479-a024-457912e9c8d5-ex1', '65808bc3-03ff-4479-a024-457912e9c8d5', 'loss', 'The team suffered a tough loss last night.', '球队昨晚遭遇了一场惨败。'),
  ('65808bc3-03ff-4479-a024-457912e9c8d5-ex2', '65808bc3-03ff-4479-a024-457912e9c8d5', 'loss', 'The insurer denied liability for losses attributable to undisclosed pre-existing conditions.', '保险公司拒绝对因未披露既往状况造成的损失承担责任。'),
  ('5100ed11-db6c-4697-bbb1-da0c48345a9e-ex1', '5100ed11-db6c-4697-bbb1-da0c48345a9e', 'degree', 'She has a degree in chemistry.', '她有化学学位。'),
  ('5100ed11-db6c-4697-bbb1-da0c48345a9e-ex2', '5100ed11-db6c-4697-bbb1-da0c48345a9e', 'degree', 'The reforms succeeded to a degree that surprised even their most ardent proponents.', '改革取得的成效连其最热心的支持者都感到意外。'),
  ('2209eaad-8b3f-4be5-b28f-517b0e6cbc9b-ex1', '2209eaad-8b3f-4be5-b28f-517b0e6cbc9b', 'wonder', 'I wonder what time it is.', '我想知道现在几点了。'),
  ('2209eaad-8b3f-4be5-b28f-517b0e6cbc9b-ex2', '2209eaad-8b3f-4be5-b28f-517b0e6cbc9b', 'wonder', 'Observers wonder whether the fragile coalition can survive the forthcoming budget negotiations.', '观察人士怀疑这个脆弱的联盟能否挺过即将到来的预算谈判。'),
  ('59f43169-5ab8-4676-90d5-eefcbff06bb3-ex1', '59f43169-5ab8-4676-90d5-eefcbff06bb3', 'attack', 'The cat attacked the toy mouse.', '猫扑向了玩具老鼠。'),
  ('59f43169-5ab8-4676-90d5-eefcbff06bb3-ex2', '59f43169-5ab8-4676-90d5-eefcbff06bb3', 'attack', 'The coordinated cyber attack disabled critical infrastructure across three provinces.', '这次协同网络攻击使三个省份的关键基础设施陷入瘫痪。'),
  ('41eb6860-a6e7-45e6-9cc6-5bb958b7088e-ex1', '41eb6860-a6e7-45e6-9cc6-5bb958b7088e', 'herself', 'She made the dress herself.', '这条裙子是她自己做的。'),
  ('41eb6860-a6e7-45e6-9cc6-5bb958b7088e-ex2', '41eb6860-a6e7-45e6-9cc6-5bb958b7088e', 'herself', 'The director herself conceded that the oversight mechanisms had proven inadequate.', '主任本人也承认，监督机制已被证明不够完善。'),
  ('b68b114e-2dac-42c6-ac8d-2eb87e4e8071-ex1', 'b68b114e-2dac-42c6-ac8d-2eb87e4e8071', 'region', 'This region is famous for its tea.', '这个地区以茶叶闻名。'),
  ('b68b114e-2dac-42c6-ac8d-2eb87e4e8071-ex2', 'b68b114e-2dac-42c6-ac8d-2eb87e4e8071', 'region', 'The agreement establishes a framework for economic integration across the entire region.', '该协议为整个地区的经济一体化确立了框架。'),
  ('3da0fc1f-fdc8-4156-9ebb-d637beaa5404-ex1', '3da0fc1f-fdc8-4156-9ebb-d637beaa5404', 'television', 'We watched the game on television.', '我们在电视上看了比赛。'),
  ('3da0fc1f-fdc8-4156-9ebb-d637beaa5404-ex2', '3da0fc1f-fdc8-4156-9ebb-d637beaa5404', 'television', 'The advent of streaming has fundamentally disrupted the traditional television industry.', '流媒体的兴起从根本上颠覆了传统电视行业。'),
  ('3968039c-e398-43db-9d76-ede04ca60e8b-ex1', '3968039c-e398-43db-9d76-ede04ca60e8b', 'box', 'Put the toys back in the box.', '把玩具放回盒子里。'),
  ('3968039c-e398-43db-9d76-ede04ca60e8b-ex2', '3968039c-e398-43db-9d76-ede04ca60e8b', 'box', 'The disclosure requirements cannot be satisfied by merely ticking a box on a standard form.', '披露要求绝非在标准表格上打个勾就能满足。'),
  ('40acbb43-5046-41c7-b9f9-4ba726c9318d-ex1', '40acbb43-5046-41c7-b9f9-4ba726c9318d', 'TV', 'Turn off the TV and do your homework.', '关掉电视去写作业。'),
  ('40acbb43-5046-41c7-b9f9-4ba726c9318d-ex2', '40acbb43-5046-41c7-b9f9-4ba726c9318d', 'TV', 'Public TV broadcasters face mounting pressure to justify their licence-fee funding models.', '公共电视广播机构面临越来越大的压力，需为其牌照费资助模式辩护。'),
  ('11a3b74f-bf49-4971-be51-63be887e9c52-ex1', '11a3b74f-bf49-4971-be51-63be887e9c52', 'training', 'He is doing training for the marathon.', '他正在为马拉松进行训练。'),
  ('11a3b74f-bf49-4971-be51-63be887e9c52-ex2', '11a3b74f-bf49-4971-be51-63be887e9c52', 'training', 'Mandatory compliance training was instituted following the regulatory censure.', '在受到监管谴责后，强制性合规培训得以制度化。'),
  ('9078e712-dc85-4285-9a37-b0c8d2bb707c-ex1', '9078e712-dc85-4285-9a37-b0c8d2bb707c', 'pretty', 'What a pretty garden!', '多漂亮的花园啊！'),
  ('9078e712-dc85-4285-9a37-b0c8d2bb707c-ex2', '9078e712-dc85-4285-9a37-b0c8d2bb707c', 'pretty', 'The projections look pretty robust even under the most pessimistic macroeconomic scenarios.', '即使在最悲观的宏观经济情景下，这些预测看起来也相当稳健。'),
  ('8824059d-cbd5-4cc3-8ec6-1821c508a215-ex1', '8824059d-cbd5-4cc3-8ec6-1821c508a215', 'trade', 'The two countries trade with each other.', '这两个国家互相做贸易。'),
  ('8824059d-cbd5-4cc3-8ec6-1821c508a215-ex2', '8824059d-cbd5-4cc3-8ec6-1821c508a215', 'trade', 'The tribunal adjudicates disputes arising under the multilateral trade agreements.', '该法庭裁决依据多边贸易协定产生的争端。'),
  ('245e4ab5-2902-4203-89af-2b0c660a4424-ex1', '245e4ab5-2902-4203-89af-2b0c660a4424', 'election', 'The election results will be announced tonight.', '选举结果今晚公布。'),
  ('245e4ab5-2902-4203-89af-2b0c660a4424-ex2', '245e4ab5-2902-4203-89af-2b0c660a4424', 'election', 'International observers certified that the election met established democratic standards.', '国际观察员认证此次选举符合既定的民主标准。'),
  ('23712e43-703e-4d2a-a82c-730ef55f5101-ex1', '23712e43-703e-4d2a-a82c-730ef55f5101', 'everybody', 'Everybody loves this song.', '大家都喜欢这首歌。'),
  ('23712e43-703e-4d2a-a82c-730ef55f5101-ex2', '23712e43-703e-4d2a-a82c-730ef55f5101', 'everybody', 'The evacuation protocol requires that everybody be accounted for within fifteen minutes.', '疏散规程要求在十五分钟内清点确认所有人员。'),
  ('89860b3b-4654-4038-a2f0-058ff816e5d1-ex1', '89860b3b-4654-4038-a2f0-058ff816e5d1', 'physical', 'Physical exercise keeps you healthy.', '体育锻炼让你保持健康。'),
  ('89860b3b-4654-4038-a2f0-058ff816e5d1-ex2', '89860b3b-4654-4038-a2f0-058ff816e5d1', 'physical', 'The audit encompassed both physical inspection of assets and verification of records.', '审计既包括对资产的实地核查，也包括对记录的核验。'),
  ('42f46d0d-3fe5-4705-a8dc-5a31f7aadeb5-ex1', '42f46d0d-3fe5-4705-a8dc-5a31f7aadeb5', 'lay', 'Lay the baby gently on the bed.', '把宝宝轻轻放在床上。'),
  ('42f46d0d-3fe5-4705-a8dc-5a31f7aadeb5-ex2', '42f46d0d-3fe5-4705-a8dc-5a31f7aadeb5', 'lay', 'The commission''s report lays the groundwork for comprehensive regulatory overhaul.', '委员会的报告为全面的监管改革奠定了基础。'),
  ('98a39a93-36b0-4a92-898a-ccb99aa8fbb1-ex1', '98a39a93-36b0-4a92-898a-ccb99aa8fbb1', 'general', 'In general, I agree with you.', '总体上我同意你的看法。'),
  ('98a39a93-36b0-4a92-898a-ccb99aa8fbb1-ex2', '98a39a93-36b0-4a92-898a-ccb99aa8fbb1', 'general', 'The general counsel advised that the proposed disclosure could prejudice pending litigation.', '总法律顾问提醒，拟议的披露可能损害未决诉讼。'),
  ('3c9e7488-6bfb-49d1-99e0-51ea3c50eb51-ex1', '3c9e7488-6bfb-49d1-99e0-51ea3c50eb51', 'feeling', 'I have a good feeling about today.', '我感觉今天会很顺利。'),
  ('3c9e7488-6bfb-49d1-99e0-51ea3c50eb51-ex2', '3c9e7488-6bfb-49d1-99e0-51ea3c50eb51', 'feeling', 'There is a growing feeling among investors that the rally has outpaced fundamentals.', '投资者中越来越多的人感到，这轮上涨已脱离基本面。'),
  ('b3e387fe-4aed-40b5-9818-b0c52852e5ef-ex1', 'b3e387fe-4aed-40b5-9818-b0c52852e5ef', 'standard', 'This hotel has a high standard of service.', '这家酒店的服务水准很高。'),
  ('b3e387fe-4aed-40b5-9818-b0c52852e5ef-ex2', 'b3e387fe-4aed-40b5-9818-b0c52852e5ef', 'standard', 'The certification scheme harmonizes safety standards across participating jurisdictions.', '该认证体系统一了参与辖区的安全标准。'),
  ('d0cc3d5f-4192-4def-a750-49dc24a12fa8-ex1', 'd0cc3d5f-4192-4def-a750-49dc24a12fa8', 'bill', 'Can we get the bill, please?', '请帮我们结账好吗？'),
  ('d0cc3d5f-4192-4def-a750-49dc24a12fa8-ex2', 'd0cc3d5f-4192-4def-a750-49dc24a12fa8', 'bill', 'The appropriations bill passed both chambers after protracted partisan negotiation.', '经过旷日持久的党派谈判，拨款法案在两院获得通过。'),
  ('7a2330d6-5aff-40dc-8407-c0b124eb16cd-ex1', '7a2330d6-5aff-40dc-8407-c0b124eb16cd', 'message', 'I left you a message on your phone.', '我在你手机上留了言。'),
  ('7a2330d6-5aff-40dc-8407-c0b124eb16cd-ex2', '7a2330d6-5aff-40dc-8407-c0b124eb16cd', 'message', 'The summit''s closing statement conveyed an unambiguous message of collective resolve.', '峰会闭幕声明传递出共同决心的明确信息。'),
  ('3312efed-9b0b-4311-8c32-fd5d869b32e4-ex1', '3312efed-9b0b-4311-8c32-fd5d869b32e4', 'fail', 'Don''t worry if you fail the first time.', '第一次失败了也别担心。'),
  ('3312efed-9b0b-4311-8c32-fd5d869b32e4-ex2', '3312efed-9b0b-4311-8c32-fd5d869b32e4', 'fail', 'Institutions that fail to meet the capital requirements face mandatory restructuring.', '未能满足资本要求的机构将面临强制重组。'),
  ('151eef4b-3b05-4655-8416-536e7c63d5e2-ex1', '151eef4b-3b05-4655-8416-536e7c63d5e2', 'outside', 'The kids are playing outside.', '孩子们在外面玩。'),
