  ('1cec251d-6ed3-4e9a-9c77-93e2f597ab88-ex1', '1cec251d-6ed3-4e9a-9c77-93e2f597ab88', 'arrive', 'What time does the train arrive?', '火车几点到？'),
  ('1cec251d-6ed3-4e9a-9c77-93e2f597ab88-ex2', '1cec251d-6ed3-4e9a-9c77-93e2f597ab88', 'arrive', 'The delegations will arrive ahead of the summit to finalize the draft communiqué.', '各代表团将先于峰会抵达，以敲定公报草案。'),
